🛡️ AI Phishing Detector

An AI-powered phishing detection system designed to identify malicious URLs, suspicious emails, and phishing-related patterns using Machine Learning techniques.

This project aims to improve cybersecurity awareness and automate phishing detection through intelligent analysis and classification models.

---

# 📌 Project Overview

Phishing attacks are one of the most common cybersecurity threats where attackers attempt to steal sensitive information through fake websites, emails, or links.

This project uses Machine Learning algorithms to analyze phishing indicators and classify whether a URL or message is:
- Legitimate
- Suspicious
- Phishing

The system focuses on combining:
- AI/ML techniques
- Feature extraction
- Cybersecurity principles
- Real-time detection concepts

---

# 🚀 Features

- ✅ AI-based phishing detection
- ✅ URL analysis and classification
- ✅ Suspicious link detection
- ✅ Feature extraction from URLs
- ✅ Machine Learning model integration
- ✅ Cybersecurity-focused workflow
- ✅ Real-time prediction capability
- ✅ User-friendly detection interface

